<h2><a id="new_sites" name="new_sites"></a>The Company of Biologists launches new journal websites</h2>
<p>The Company of Biologists has migrated its leading journals to the hosting platform of Silverchair, improving user experience and maximising the discoverability of their content for the biological community.</p>
<p>The Silverchair Platform now hosts The Company of Biologists' five influential journals: Development, Journal of Cell Science, Journal of Experimental Biology, Disease Models &amp; Mechanisms, and Biology Open. The journal websites, available via <a href="https://journals.biologists.com">journals.biologists.com</a> have been given an updated, modern design, with additional functionalities, such as split-screen view for easy data reference. Moving platforms has also given the Company’s journals access to a range of partner integrations via the Silverchair Universe.</p>
