<h2><strong><a id="movies" name="movies"></a></strong>Play-in-place movies now available in Journal of Experimental Biology</h2>
<p>Journal of Experimental Biology, along with the other journals of The Company of Biologists, has recently introduced the option of playing movies in place in the full text online version of its articles. This means that videos can now be an integral part of any article and that they are placed into the full text online version of the article, making it easier and quicker for readers to access this type of content. In order to provide this service we have partnered with <a href="https://glencoesoftware.com/index.html" target="_blank">Glencoe Software</a>.</p>
<p>See <a href="../article/221/4/jeb169466/33954/" target="_blank">an example of an article with a play-in-place movie</a>.</p>
